# Environment Variables

## Backend (Render)
```bash
# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:port/database

# Server
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=production
```

## Frontend (Vercel)
```bash
# API URL - Point to your Render backend
VITE_API_URL=https://dgmarket-crm.onrender.com

# For local development, leave empty or use:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
```

## Local Development
Create a `.env` file in the project root:
```bash
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://localhost:5432/marketcrm
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development
```

Frontend will automatically use same-origin requests when `VITE_API_URL` is not set.
